inventory.special_mentions: Sale Price includes a $1000 finance credit when financed at Capital Subaru. Capital Subaru is pleased to offer the Capital Verified Pre-Owned Program. This program is designed to offer you confidence and peace of mind throughout your buying journey. When you choose a Capital Verified vehicle, you can expect not only superior quality but also an extensive range of benefits to ensure your complete satisfaction. What’s included with your Capital Verified Program Vehicle? - 7-Day/500km Exchange Privilege (equal or greater value) - Lifetime Powertrain Warranty - 160 Multi-Point Inspection & Report - CARFAX Report - 3-Month Sirius XM Subscription - Professional Detailing with Fluid Top-up + Gas - 10% Off Set of Tires (discount applied at the time of purchase, up to a maximum of $100) - Seasonal Tire Storage (1 season)

With rock-solid reliability and a nicely broken-in quality, Subaru Certified Pre-Owned Vehicles have years of reliable miles ahead of them. These vehicles come standard with significant advantages over non-certified, used Subaru models, including factory warranties, 24-hour roadside assistance programs and detailed inspections from factory-trained Subaru technicians. Subaru Certified Pre-Owned Vehicles meet the highest standards for safety, security and overall performance – in other words, the standards you’ve come to expect from Subaru. Powered by a wide range of added benefits, the Subaru Certified Pre-Owned Program also eliminates many of the worries typically associated with purchasing a used vehicle.
